title: Halfway v1.1.2
description:
Halfway 1.1.2

Extract 7zip & play!



Changes:

    A graphics option has been added which allows to disable the UI color displacement effect. 

Bug fixes:

    Fixed Jenna's Berserk skill consuming both AP when used to shoot at more than one target. It's now using only 1 AP as intended.
    Fixed weapon reload possible in combat with zero AP via the inventory screen, causing unwanted side effects.
